  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Education_StudentDB系统做一个混合线程调度的甘特图，重点是展示GradeSync和StudentDB两个服务之间的交互。我想分成三个处理器P1、P2、P3来展示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "Hilos Mixtos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，P1对应GradeSync，P2和P3都归StudentDB管。时间轴用毫秒单位可以吗？我看到有几个关键阶段：执行期、IO等待、还有ULT用户级线程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1 (Education_GradeSync)",
        "P2 (Education_StudentDB)",
        "P3 (Education_StudentDB)",
        "axisFormat",
        "ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，毫秒合适。P1上先跑T1的执行段，然后进入IO阻塞。P2和P3要展示T1和T2的交错执行，特别是P3的T2要用ULT模式——标记成done状态，表示已经完成的用户级线程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "P1-T1_IO",
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "P2-T2_exec",
        "P3-T2_ULT",
        "done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出三个section的主体结构。P1-T1_exec从0开始跑4毫秒，active状态；然后P1-T1_IO从第6毫秒开始，标记为crit。P2那边T1从第4毫秒接手，T2执行段放到12-14毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "p1t1a",
        "0, 4",
        "P1-T1_IO",
        "p1t1io",
        "6, 9",
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "p2t1a",
        "4, 8"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，P2的T2还需要一个IO段，从14到16毫秒，也是crit标记。另外P3的T1执行要覆盖8到12毫秒，和P3-T2_ULT完全重叠——这正好体现ULT和内核线程的并发区别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_IO",
        "p2t2io",
        "14, 16",
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "p3t1a",
        "P3-T2_ULT",
        "p3t2ult",
        "8, 12"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了。P2-T2_IO用crit标红，P3那边两个条带都压在8-12毫秒区间。现在需要处理到达事件吗？我看有六个里程碑式的到达点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_IO",
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "P3-T2_ULT",
        "Llegadas",
        "milestone"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
